<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Jul1932"><font color="red">21 July 1932</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Today&apos;s news from Germany will probably upset my wife &hellip; In all this muddle I wrote to Eliot, offering to refund the &pound;150 advanced on <i>Work in Progress</i> and cancel the contract &hellip; who could work in such a whirl of worries </div>
